with info    cite 'perl module to handle meta information in image files
Image::ExifTool is a customizable set of Perl libraries
plus an application script for reading and writing meta
information in image, audio and video files, including
the maker note information of many digital cameras by
various manufacturers such as Canon, Casio, FujiFilm,
JVC/Victor, Kodak, Leaf, Minolta/Konica-Minolta, Nikon,
Olympus/Epson, Panasonic/Leica, Pentax/Asahi, Ricoh,
Sanyo and Sigma/Foveon.'
